query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 10 AND q.view_count <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('android-recyclerview',
'bufferedreader',
'calendar',
'ckeditor',
'compiler-errors',
'dart',
'facebook-graph-api',
'google-calendar-api',
'jetty',
'listener',
'progress-bar',
'sql-injection',
'storyboard',
'treeview',
'wamp');
